text: Vaidotas is a Lithuanian masculine given name. The diminutive of the name is Vaidas. People with the name Vaidotas include: *Vaidotas (fl. 1362), Lithuanian noble, son of Kęstutis, Grand Duke of Lithuania *Vaidotas Šilėnas (born 1985), Lithuanian footballer *Vaidotas Šlekys (born 1972), Lithuanian footballer ==References== Category:Lithuanian masculine given names
title: Vaidotas (name)
